---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: About
description: Two-decade engineering career across global commerce, RBI-regulated FinTech, and multilingual public computing; standards work; independent research.
---
<article class="about">

  <header>
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Engineering executive and systems thinker.</h1>
  </header>

  <section>
    {% set bio = bios.long.split("\n\n") %}
    {% for p in bio %}<p{% if loop.first %} class="lede"{% endif %}>{{ p }}</p>{% endfor %}

    <figure class="portrait">
      {% portrait "anivar.jpg", "Anivar A. Aravind, head-and-shoulders portrait." %}
      <figcaption>Photograph reproduced with permission. <span class="muted">[TODO: photographer credit]</span></figcaption>
    </figure>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="career">
    <h2 id="career">Operator career</h2>
    <ul class="t-list">
      {% set currently = log | byCareerGroup('currently') %}
      {% set recent = log | byCareerGroup('recent') %}
      {% set earlier = log | byCareerGroup('earlier') %}
      {% if currently.length %}
        <li class="group-label">Currently</li>
        <li><ul class="rows">{% for r in currently %}<li><span class="role">{{ r.title }}{% if r.org %}, {{ r.org }}{% endif %}</span><span class="span">{{ r | spanLabel }}</span></li>{% endfor %}</ul></li>
      {% endif %}
      {% if recent.length %}
        <li class="group-label">Recent</li>
        <li><ul class="rows">{% for r in recent | reverse %}<li><span class="role">{{ r.title }}{% if r.org %}, {{ r.org }}{% endif %}</span><span class="span">{{ r | spanLabel }}</span></li>{% endfor %}</ul></li>
      {% endif %}
      {% if earlier.length %}
        <li class="group-label">Earlier</li>
        <li><ul class="rows">{% for r in earlier %}<li><span class="role">{{ r.title }}{% if r.org %}, {{ r.org }}{% endif %}</span><span class="span">{{ r | spanLabel }}</span></li>{% endfor %}</ul></li>
      {% endif %}
    </ul>
    <p class="muted">
      Multi-region delivery across the UK, India, and global operations. Regulated FinTech operating
      experience covering PCI&nbsp;DSS, PSD2/SCA, 3DS, and RBI NBFC compliance. M&amp;A and technical
      diligence experience on both sides of the table. Multi-site engineering org leadership: hiring,
      levelling, performance management, succession planning. Monolith → modular / API-first /
      event-driven transformation at Kinara Capital. 3.75× growth, one product to five, as SVP
      Engineering at Kinara. 10,000+ branded apps on a shared platform across six markets in global
      commerce.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="standards">
    <h2 id="standards">Standards, policy, and governance</h2>
    <ul class="t-list">
      <li><ul class="rows">
        {% for r in log | byCareerGroup('standards') | reverse %}
          <li><span class="role">{{ r.title }}{% if r.org %}, {{ r.org }}{% endif %}</span><span class="span">{{ r | spanLabel }}</span></li>
        {% endfor %}
        {% for r in log | byKind('standard') %}
          <li><span class="role">Co-author, {{ r.title }}{% if r.org %} ({{ r.org }}){% endif %}</span><span class="span">{{ r | spanLabel }}</span></li>
        {% endfor %}
        {% for r in log | byKind('award') %}
          <li><span class="role">{{ r.title }}{% if r.org %}, {{ r.org }}{% endif %}</span><span class="span">{{ r | spanLabel }}</span></li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="muted">Worked on ECMAScript 2025 conformance via Mozilla Rhino. ICANN UASG and Neo-Brahmi Generation Panel contributor.</p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="independent">
    <h2 id="independent">Independent collective work</h2>
    <ul class="wi-list">
      {% for w in log | byTheme('collective') %}
        <li>
          <p class="name">{{ w.title }}</p>
          <div class="body">
            <p class="scope">{{ w.scope }}</p>
            <p class="desc">{{ w.role }} · {{ w | spanLabel }}</p>
            <p class="link"><a href="{{ w.external or w.internalHref }}">{{ (w.external or w.internalHref) | replace("https://", "") | replace("http://", "") }}</a></p>
          </div>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <p class="muted"><a href="/projects/">Independent projects and writing →</a></p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="education">
    <h2 id="education">Education</h2>
    <p>Cochin University of Science and Technology — B.Tech, Information Technology. 2001 – 2005.</p>
  </section>

</article>
